# Yashigani release signing key — SSH allowed-signers format
#
# Signing method: SSH (git tag -s with gpg.format=ssh)
# Key type:       ed25519
# Signer:         Maxine <maxine@agnosticsec.com>
# Used since:     v2.23.3
#
# To verify a signed release tag locally:
#
#   git config gpg.ssh.allowedSignersFile docs/release-signing-key.pub
#   git tag -v v2.23.3
#
# The allowed-signers line below follows the OpenSSH allowed_signers(5) format:
#   <principal> namespaces="git" <keytype> <base64-key>
#
# Only "git" namespace tags are covered; SSH authentication use of this key
# for host access is a separate concern not governed by this file.
#
